to avoid the lawsuit due to the evidence.

112
00:05:38,990 --> 00:05:42,060
While I was searching for a lawyer,

113
00:05:42,060 --> 00:05:45,880
I came across Hakamada-sensei,
a specialist in divorce issues.

114
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:51,720
Then, I found out he's is the son
of my father and his former wife.

115
00:05:54,550 --> 00:05:58,060
So I thought he would be the only
one suitable to take this case.

116
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:01,160
Please, Sensei.

117
00:06:01,670 --> 00:06:04,300
