257
00:12:26,490 --> 00:12:28,060
Oh, Natsuki-san.

258
00:12:28,060 --> 00:12:30,520
Did my father come here?

259
00:12:30,520 --> 00:12:32,820
He was just here.

260
00:12:32,820 --> 00:12:35,040
